#
# Template. Copy to `.kamal/secrets` (gitignored) and fill in real
# values, OR keep this shell-expansion form and `export` the vars
# in the shell where you call `kamal`.
#
# Generate fresh values:
#   POSTGRES_PASSWORD=$(openssl rand -hex 24)
#   ERLANG_COOKIE=$(openssl rand -hex 32)
#
# KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD = GitHub PAT (classic) with `read:packages`.

KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD=$KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=$POSTGRES_PASSWORD
DB_PASS=$DB_PASS
ERLANG_COOKIE=$ERLANG_COOKIE
